column3: “I love this stuff! I typically only rate strains that offer a unique experience - uplifting but mellow, etc. This is just a good old-fashioned, knock your dick in the dirt, THC high! What makes this one unique is its potency - just a few solid puffs and you'll be ready to veg out to The Simpsons while eating cereal straight from the box. This flower is to be cared for, from infancy to ingestion. This is the kind of f...”

“This is hands down my favorite strain. I've been smoking regularly for a few years now, and never has a strain given me the same level of stoned in just the first rip as Alien OG. This strain is perfect if you just want to chill around, or if you have errands to run. The high always gives me a similar feeling of reality as skyrim if that makes sense. Like you feel in a different world, a video game world. It makes ot...”
“So dank, no one can hear you scream.”

“i have been a connoisseur of ganja for the last 10 years. i am very strict when examining quality and consistency of the flowers and concentrates I medicate on. first time trying Alien OG shatter and boy this is CREAM OF THE CROP if you are getting a authentic batch. the concentrate kinda crept up on me within 10-15 minutes. the fade started with a warm and fuzzy feeling in my eye lids, incredibly relaxed, very eupho...”

“I am a daily smoker and this strain just mind raped me. It was like a swirling storm of ideas and sensations in my head. Every thought was disassembled and finely tuned...then just as quickly forgotten and moving on to the next thing. The body high is melty but I would not recommend this if you need to pay attention to anything. This one is quite powerful, intense and all encompassing. The perfect weed for situations...”

“This is a very nice strain, with very frosty buds and a beautiful light green color. Very strong in THC and has a very loud smell, but overall it's gets you super high and the high is a very uplifted high.... so yeah it's super dank.”

“I gotta tell you this is my go-to med. I have nerve damage in my head that causes insane migraines so I'm always looking for a Sativa or Sativa dom Hyb but sometimes they just put you on the moon (Jack, White Widow etc.) which is great if you don't have to actually like communicate with anyone. I work in technology and have to be coherent all day, run conference calls, think through problems and this strain allows my...”
“Holy shit.”

“day 4

woke up took 4 hits off my clay chillum

and havs  a strong body high

i feel loose with like no attachment to anything

this is great”

“I think its really fun weed because it made me so hungry I could eat an alien. And this was not average pot , its fairly high quality weed so I ate another one. It totally makes everything taste and feel better.”
“Ummmm.... ..  .. . . . ........ . . . . wow. What were we talking about?”
“Top 10 favorite highs. makes all the pain and stress dissapear instantaneously... This earthy flower is one to remember not just the high but the aromatic pungent smell is one of my favorites”

“I got home from the emergency room 5 hours ago. Symptoms: flank pain so intense that I barfed. Diagnosis: 5mm kidney stone. 

Cool. 

Smoked some Alien OG about 10 mins ago and I'm laying on my bed listening to music. I feel only a little pain and my body is very relaxed. Everything is vibrating. I feel sleepy, but it is closer to a deep relaxation than an actual need for sleep. 

Very nice body high and equally amaz...”

“This stuff smells really good but is very indica dominated. So if indicas are your weapon of choice, this strain is for you. This stuff is strictly for relaxing and just chilling . You will be couch locked with this strain for sure. I straight up melted into a massage chair. This stuff is also great for insomnia and pain relief. Definitely makes for some sleepy boat times!”

“This was my first time with alien OG , it came into my life about two or three weeks ago. Man do I love this flower, not only did it give me a little energy boost but it also put my ass to sleep!
Great for nighttime smoke sessions.
Ill rate a view things 
Sleepy 8 out of 10
Taste : 9 out of 10
Smell:  8 out of 10
High:   9 out of 10
Duration: about 2 hours if you don't fall asleep.”

“phenomenal smoke and very smooth. Aromas of fruit and cloves are present in the thick smoke, and the effects kick in quickly. Makes one feel a little spacy and makes one slightly hallucinate. Although you will be spaced out you will still be able to move normally and focus fine. Good for before sleeping. Much euphoria and pain relief is noted. overall a very strong and pleasant smoke.”

“Racy come on...thoughts start flying around like you’ve had too much caffeine. It’s not “bad” though. There’s just a lot of unbridled energy deep inside. As the high swiftly progresses, a numb layer surrounding you continues to expand to the point of wiping out your brain. You can feel mental faculties going blank, staring absently, unsure what you were doing again. There’s an edge that’s a little too real. It’s loos...”

“Alien OG is one of my new favorite strains!!  I am typically an indica or indica dominant lover, but there are times when you want a good Hybrid for social situations and this is good for that.  But the most interesting thing I love the most about this strain is how when I hit my pipe, I can feel my lungs expanding but there's no tickle in my throat making me cough.  I don't care for lines that make you cough, and I'...”

“I love this stuff it tastes like pine I smoked 5 bowls of mids and didn't feel shit I smoked one bowl of this and I was fucked! I got stopped by the cops while hitting a g bong and I was soo high we talked our way out of a trip to jail and a ticket it's my favorite by far!!!”

“WOW!  I have been smoking for pain for about two years now and I feel like I have tried every strain under the sun, looking for one that really makes a difference for pain.  This is the first time that a strain has completely taken it away.  A lot of strains will touch it a little but never has one taken it completely away, like Alien OG.  I have been smoking it for three days now and there is such a huge difference....”

“Hands down one of the best strains ive ever smoked. The smell is very piney, but slightly sweet, and tastes exceptionally good. Usually i have to smoke several bong bowls to get a nice high, but after one bowl i was super relaxed and incredibly high. I couldn't believe the head and body high i had after only one bowl! It felt so nice to relax and simply socialize and watch movies, however it also felt enticing to go ...”
“Very stoney, euphoric high, will leave you giggling at random objects on the carpet.  Great social strain.  Only drawback is that it's pretty skunky, so not a good strain for discrete use.”

“This blend made me feel so connected to everyone and every thing. It was an amazing feeling; like I was effortlessly
gliding through existence on this world. There's definitely an Existential component to this strong strain. Perfect  for  when you want to feel as one with the universe.”

“One of my favorite go-to strains! It's similar to Blue Dream in giving a visually-oriented high that is wonderful for night-time walks with headphones. Low in paranoia, often spurs creative thoughts, keeps me happy and motivated, and not much of a body high makes it perfect for an active yet chill evening at home- take a bath, do some creative writing, go for a walk, and so forth. Not inherently social like some stra...”

“I recently have been looking for a nice balances hybrid since I suffer from symptoms where sometimes I have insomnia and can't go to sleep. Other times I'm too tired & fatigued to do anything.  

Aroma 9/10
Has very noticeable pine lemon zest smell that reminds me OG kush. 

Flavor 9/10
I can taste an almost citrus favor, nothing spectacular though.

Effects 9/10
If I need to function yet still need powerful medicina...”
“Dry mouth is definitely real with this one. Gives a very relaxed high and once you get into a giggle fit it'll be a bit before you stop.”
“Just smoked some Alien OG - wow!  Great high - creative - got chores done with happiness and energy.  Great stony high - very easy coming down...I definitely recommend if you like a cerebral high.”

“daaamn this shit is the bomb! on my birthday my friend rolled a joint of alien o.g for me an that shit got my ass so stoned that i smoked it at 8 in the morning and the feeling came down after school lol. this has 5 out of 5 for me”

“If you have problems getting to sleep then this is it! I get a good body buzz after about 7 -10 minutes into a session. I find it hard to stay awake after vaping with this strain. It also gives me a weed hangover with headache sometimes.”

“Lovely strain, the batch I had was fluffy with red hairs on and the nugs were caked in THC, the nugs were dense and crumbled easilly.. the smell - you could definitely smell some lemon but it had an earthy undertone.. the taste was very similar. The affect - the affect was very euphoric and gave a full body high (making my legs randomly twitch after a bedtime joint) it was also a very relaxing head high.. definitely ...”

“Bitter taste, great high. Very light, mostly heady. J and I rolled some up into a grape blunt and on one of the first cool evenings in Georgia smoked until we didn't care how our throats felt. Right behind my eyes, that's where mr alien really has control. One of the better highs I've had in a long time. This could be one of the best strains I've never smoked, then again maybe it's just the cool breeze.”

“This review is on Alien OG flower, by Native Roots. 

I had never tried Alien OG prior to snagging this O from Native and wow.  Its appearance as well as smell resembles their Bruce Banner.  It's buds have the traditional OG structure and are covered in white crystal-like trichomes with extremely dark shades of black/blue and dark orange hairs.  The terps are a sweeter earth/pine flavor which is why I compared them t...”

“This strain gives me a sense of relief and peace of mind. I enjoy that I can medicate at home and get couch locked and feel it throughout, but also be able to medicate before exercising or going out, without being totally phased. Tis a gewd strain!”

“I've heard many mixed reviews about this strain, and when a friend of mine offered to give me a free eighth, I just couldn't resist. My first impressions (upon smoking a bowl in my bong) were very positive; I liked the way the smoke tasted, the texture of the buds, the color, the way it burned, it was all very appealing from the start. It smelled very nice too. Meanwhile, the actual high was strange; for me, it start...”
“Awesome for PMS relief ladies!”

“All I know about this strain is I took it mixed with a Jedi kush vape bowl. And it's great.. you get the nice effect of the indica.. perfect body paralyzer. Whole body feels like it's floating..'then you begin to feel the effects of the Alien OG, the real star.. literally, on a star because you don't know where you are.. your body is floating in the universe inside your own house.. you feel deep in space and complete...”

“GREAT OG (Alien Technology x Tahoe OG)

Great example of genetic science. This is similar to Tahoe OG but with a little more head euphoria. Great Mid - Night strain. Will knock out in large amounts.

60% Sativa”
“Very distinct taste and smell. Got me blazed quickly and is a pretty bud.”

“Ive been smoking for 3 amazing years, and to this day, Alien OG has remained my favorite strain. My first time using this strain was 2 years ago, and I will never forget how unbelievably high I was. I remember packing about 5 bong-loads at a pond and after that all I remember is I awoke" from being basically subconscious. When I regained my composure I was on the total opposite side of my town
“I call it a good solid 8.. I felt very spacey. thought I was from another planet haha.. really good strand.. nice colors, fluffy buds”

“Daily smokers rejoice as this strain does the job & more. Lots of Kush goodness here with the parents being Alien Kush & Tahoe OG Kush. My dense medium green buds with dark orange hairs packed 22% THC. The scent was pine/lemon/skunk & the flavor was a bit spicy but, nice. Best thing about this strain was the effects. Start off & everything is sharper and clearer with all senses. I was happy & euphoric while being upl...”

“All I know about this strain is I took it mixed with a Jedi kush vape bowl. And it's great.. you get the nice effect of the indica.. perfect body paralyzer. Whole body feels like it's floating..'then you begin to feel the effects of the Alien OG, the real star.. literally, on a star because you don't know where you are.. your body is floating in the universe inside your own house.. you feel deep in space and complete...”

“Alien Og one of my new favorites. I'll start with the smell it is strong and pungent you can smell it through almost anything my house has been taken over by the aroma. It's sticky with trichromes  all over the loose fluffy buds. I love to cough and this sure will make you do that. Very good high euphoric lightheadedness hits you immediately and then soon after takes the whole body over with a relaxed but not sleepy,...”
“This strain makes me feel tingly and excited like a kid waking up on Christmas morning.”
“Very distinct taste and smell. Got me blazed quickly and is a pretty bud.”

“This strain is an indica dominant strain. The effects are very relaxing, mild to high euphoria, and it feels as if you just arrived in a different planet. Good for evening to night use, it will keep you calm, yet not couch locked. Your mind will be stimulated as well. A really good one to try. It is quite unique.”
“smoked a 2g blunt w this, plus some girl scout cookies. I was really f**** stoned off my ass.”

“I was hesitant to try this strain for the first time. I'm a true believer in sticking with what I know works. My oh my, am I glad I tried this one. 
It's a bit of a creeper, but you feel the relaxation effects of it very soon. At that point it's up to you to stop, or keep going and explore the universe. 
This is a good strain for a clear minded experience. Though you will probably feel a couch locked. Fight that urge...”
“Amazing high lasted for a while and the taste was pretty decent”
“Love it! Spaced out on the alien OG! Slept like a rock which was what I hoped!”

“Day two
smoked 2 joints today felt great
body was relaxed i went to the pool and just floated it was quite something
so far i recommend this to relax and unwind 
its almost puts me in a full meditative state”

“Bought a gram pre-roll of this on a whim and was one of the absolute best highs I've ever had. Hit me more like an indica (read: couchlocked under a cocoon of blankets) but also came with a killer head high that kept my mind active. Put on alt-J's this is all yours on my beats and was the first time I felt like I could literally FEEL an album in my head...fucking brilliant! Will definitely be back for more.”

“I've suffered from chronic migraines and inflammation in my neck since childhood. After one bowl, 10 minutes in, I started to feel a delightful relaxing in my shoulders. My temples began to lose some tension and my jaw quit clenching on its own. 20 minutes in, I was standing tall and doing the dishes. I was able to hold an in depth conversation and the energy was fabulous. I would highly recommend this as a pain figh...”
“High THC percentage”

“This had me just happy. No worries at all. Stress was a long forgotten memory. Pain melted away as this buzz took hold in my lower back. If you just wanna chill and laugh on the couch this is perfect.”

“I’m high off this right now... I don’t even know what to say. Im just chilling feeling really good. It’s also making me feel like I need to be doing something to keep my brain active. Lol that didn’t make any sense, but I’m yeah I’m high. I recommend this strain to anyone who wants to be in a chill mellow / jolly mood. I rolled a joint btw,”

“First timer with this strain. Dark fluffy nugs with a lemony-piney scent. While its listed as an indica, I found the effects to be more appropriately placed between pure indicas and hybrids. The initial inhale produced a sharp hit to the back of the throat that almost had me reaching for a water bottle. Subsequent tokes were much kinder. This is a very potent strain. I'm unaware of the THC levels but this strain prod...”

“Excellent even for us old salty smokers.”

“I have cptsd(along with other health issues) and made the mistake of seeing someone I shouldn't have at Christmas. I wasn't sleeping, and when I was, I was having the same nightmare over and over. 
I informed the bud tender of what was going on and that none of the strains I had on hand were working, explaining that indicas typically calm me down enough to give me energy when I'm feeling this badly, and I start clean...”

“It smells great. Like a mixture of baked cookies, but with no specific flavoring.

Its initial taste is very soft and leisurely as it spreads throughout. 

I smoked it with a bowl, and the high I received was very chill. All too often I find bud that goes straight to the head but this is more of an 'enhancing' strain for music, tv, etc consumption. It is probably very fun to have a depthy conversion about thought-pro...”

body was relaxed i went to the pool and just floated it was quite something
so far i recommend this to relax and unwind

Beyond that, the smell is nice and piney, it's hairs are nice thick an orange and it's very frosty underneath it all.”
“Amazing high lasted for a while and the taste was pretty decent”

“The description is on point. But to add to that, I found that the come down gave me a very relaxed sensation. As if I were on vacation at a resort. Great strain for trying to relieve any sort of tension in the mind and body.”
“Just got this strain in from San Jose. And it's probably the best tasting weed and the best high I've gotten out of my 4 years of smoking all day everyday.”
“Nice pine 🌲 taste. good buzz that creeps up on you and gets you energized. great day time bud. effects last hour -2 then gotta smoke another.”
“Love this strain! I’m a sufferer of a stress disorder and it almost knocked it out completely! Definitely recommend!”

“Very good hybrid, took effect about 15 min later, creeps slowly and is stronger than average. Smooth refreshing citrus pine taste, reminds me of when I have a vodka & energy drink. A nice sleepy feeling with a slight uppity feeling & relaxing. Happy it helped my back and leg pain. A good do a couple things around the house then nap and have sweet dreams strain... Zzz”

“Taste: To me it started out lemony and midway through a mild blue cheese. Sounds odd, but it works at the end. 

I suffer from chronic pain, this strain knocks the pain out. It makes me feel good, slightly uplifting, but super chill at the he same time.
It makes me want to throw on a good comedy special and laugh my ass off for a couple hours...”

If you have a chance to medicate with this strain then you should do so or you're screwing yourself out of one of the great SoCal hybrid...”

“One of the strongest strains out there - reportedly showing THC as high as 28%.  Smell is peppery and unique but the smoke was somewhat unremarkable.  However the effects are remarkable.  This strain will knock even the most experienced user's socks off.”

column3:
“It smells great. Like a mixture of baked cookies, but with no specific flavoring.

Its initial taste is very soft and leisurely as it spreads throughout. 

I smoked it with a bowl, and the high I received was very chill. All too often I find bud that goes straight to the head but this is more of an 'enhancing' strain for music, tv, etc consumption. It is probably very fun to have a depthy conversion about thought-pro...”
“Me and my friends took two hits each of the Alien OG and watched two episodes of Trailer Park Boys totally couch locked. Felt like we were on another planet, no wonder it's called Alien.”

The Tahoe stands out as does the alien, strong body...”
